  "detailed_description": "An exhilarating VR game with a new sensation where you take down many enemy robots with sword slashes.<br>「SLASH OF BULLET」<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/e01b1c926a961378e22979285eb1c3ec.poster.avif?t=1726577894\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/e01b1c926a961378e22979285eb1c3ec.webm?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/e01b1c926a961378e22979285eb1c3ec.mp4?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You only have a single sword to fight the numerous attacking enemies.<br>Throw flying slashes to cut down all enemies and bullets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/c820576169a522ec96081a9dc3ca787d.poster.avif?t=1726577894\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/c820576169a522ec96081a9dc3ca787d.webm?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/c820576169a522ec96081a9dc3ca787d.mp4?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>By acquiring better skills, you can strengthen the slashes or weaken your enemies.<br>Find your best combination of skills and aim for a higher score!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/9e9bbbdca3507e154acb08200653abec.poster.avif?t=1726577894\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/9e9bbbdca3507e154acb08200653abec.webm?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/9e9bbbdca3507e154acb08200653abec.mp4?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Combine specific skills to acquire special skills.<br>It will greatly change your sword's appearance and performance, and you can beat the enemy with overwhelming power!",
  "about_the_game": "An exhilarating VR game with a new sensation where you take down many enemy robots with sword slashes.<br>「SLASH OF BULLET」<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/e01b1c926a961378e22979285eb1c3ec.poster.avif?t=1726577894\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/e01b1c926a961378e22979285eb1c3ec.webm?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/e01b1c926a961378e22979285eb1c3ec.mp4?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You only have a single sword to fight the numerous attacking enemies.<br>Throw flying slashes to cut down all enemies and bullets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/c820576169a522ec96081a9dc3ca787d.poster.avif?t=1726577894\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/c820576169a522ec96081a9dc3ca787d.webm?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/c820576169a522ec96081a9dc3ca787d.mp4?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>By acquiring better skills, you can strengthen the slashes or weaken your enemies.<br>Find your best combination of skills and aim for a higher score!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/9e9bbbdca3507e154acb08200653abec.poster.avif?t=1726577894\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/9e9bbbdca3507e154acb08200653abec.webm?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559790/extras/9e9bbbdca3507e154acb08200653abec.mp4?t=1726577894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Combine specific skills to acquire special skills.<br>It will greatly change your sword's appearance and performance, and you can beat the enemy with overwhelming power!",
